    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Heavy silver Byzantine coins worth six scruples, one twelfth of a gold solidus, and issued from the early 7th to the early 8th century.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
